{"tid":697750,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"杜蘭特：當你的身邊都是偉大的球員時，想要脫穎而出就更困難","createTime":"2018-06-11T07:05:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T08:33:17.000Z","uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ce614748a53d6dca86f6a9d50eb4ead57c1cad1b","tid":697750,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T07:05:36.000Z","msg":"「我覺得當你的身邊沒有優秀的球員時，你很容易成為最好的球員。但是當你的身邊都是偉大的球員時，想要脫穎而出就更困難。」Durant說道，「我為自己感到驕傲的是，無論我在哪裡打球，我都能脫穎而出。無論我在哪裡打球，我都努力訓練。我覺得這些球員們都接受了我，我覺得我是一名勇士球員。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thescore.com/nba/news/1484261?utm_source=dlvr.it&amp;utm_medium=twitter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thescore.com%2Fnba%2Fnews%2F1484261%3Futm_source%3Ddlvr.it%26utm_medium%3Dtwitter&d=kPKbtd5N3Rv9bYbNO5%2FJ526kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=b8b70065\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thescore.com/nba/news/1484261?utm_source=dlvr.it&amp;utm_medium=twitter</a>"},{"pid":"95f33201a31108703ef89fff2d2f7b5f1785de87","tid":697750,"uid":70846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T08:33:17.000Z","msg":"叫Curry情何以堪？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}